# C++
**/cmake-build*/
**/build*/
**/*.so
**/*.log*

# Omniverse
**/*.dmp
**/.thumbs

# No USD files allowed in the repo
**/*.usd
**/*.usda
**/*.usdc
**/*.usdz

# Python
.DS_Store
**/*.egg-info/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
